# ✅ 4. How This Works (Flow)

    1. useInfiniteQuery → fetch paginated API
    2. Data stored in pages
    3. Flatten pages → list of items

    4. react-window:
       → renders only visible rows ✅

    5. IntersectionObserver:
       → detects scroll bottom
       → fetchNextPage()

    Result:
    ✔ smooth scrolling
    ✔ fewer DOM elements
    ✔ optimized network calls

